<div id="review_9553845" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/9553845" />
    <a title="Joe S" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/633622-joe-s"><img alt="Joe S" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1196169633p2/633622.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/9553845?book_show_action=true">Nov 26, 2007</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Joe S" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Joe S" href="/user/show/633622-joe-s">Joe S</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="did not like it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">did not like it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/633622-joe-s?shelf=novels">novels</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer9553845" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8555686008533903974">What a colossal waste of my life. Nothing happens. Literally. That&apos;s what&apos;s wrong with this book. It&apos;s a freshman-level fiction workshop gone horribly awry. And it won <i>what</i>?</span>
  <span id="freeText8555686008533903974" style="display:none">What a colossal waste of my life. Nothing happens. Literally. That's what's wrong with this book. It's a freshman-level fiction workshop gone horribly awry. And it won <i>what</i>?</span>
  <a data-text-id="8555686008533903974" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


